msgid "Bugs fixed"
msgstr "Исправленные ошибки"

msgid "Core"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"``fiber.cond:wait()`` now correctly throws an error when a fiber is "
"cancelled, instead of ignoring the timeout and returning without any signs "
"of an error (gh-5013)."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Fixed a memory corruption issue, which was most visible on macOS, but could "
"affect any system (gh-5312)."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"A dynamic module now gets correctly unloaded from memory in case of an "
"attempt to load a non-existing function from it (gh-5475)."
msgstr ""

msgid "A ``swim:quit()`` call now can’t result in a crash (gh-4570)."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Snapshot recovery with no JSONPath or multikey indices involved now has "
"normal performance (gh-4774)."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"A false-positive “too long WAL write” message no longer appears for "
"synchronous transactions (gh-5139)."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"A ``box.ctl.wait_rw()`` call could return when the instance was not in fact "
"writable due to having foreign synchronous transactions. As a result, there "
"was no proper way to wait until the automatically elected leader would "
"become writable. Now ``box.ctl.wait_rw()`` works correctly (gh-5440)."
msgstr ""

msgid "SQL"
msgstr ""

msgid "Data changes in read-only mode are now forbidden (gh-5231)."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Query execution now doesn’t occasionally raise an unrelated error “Space ‘0’"
" does not exist” (gh-5592)."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Coinciding names of temporary files (used to store data during execution) "
"having two instances running on the same machine no longer cause a segfault "
"(gh-5537)."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"The return value of ``ifnull()`` built-in function is now of a correct type."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"SQL calling Lua functions with box calls inside can no longer result in a "
"memory corruption (gh-5427)."
msgstr ""

msgid "LuaJIT"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Dispatching ``__call`` metamethod no longer causes address clashing "
"(gh-4518, gh-4649)."
msgstr ""

msgid "Fixed a false positive panic when yielding in debug hook (gh-5649)."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"An attempt to use a ``net.box`` connection which is not established yet now "
"results in a correctly reported error (gh-4787)."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Fixed a ``NULL`` dereference on error paths in merger which usually happened"
" on a ‘wrong’ ``key_def`` (gh-5450)."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Calling ``key_def.compare_with_key()`` with an invalid key no longer causes "
"a segfault (gh-5307)."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Fixed a hang which occured when ``tarantool`` ran a user script with the "
"``-e`` option and this script exited with an error (like with ``tarantool -e"
" 'assert(false)'``) (gh-4983)."
msgstr ""

